Class PaAttributeValueForwardingEnabledBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.PaAttributeValueForwardingEnabledBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>, PaAttributeValueForwardingEnabledBuilder

    public class PaAttributeValueForwardingEnabledBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaAttributeValueForwardingEnabledBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement traffic forwarding status attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
